text.tspan: For the second part of this module we had to go into groups
and come up with an idea that would be aesthically pleasing. We
decided to do a campaign against smoking. For the group task I
had to create a Kill Smoking website.
I had to make sure that the font was readable, clear and and the colour
scheme was user friendly as our target audience was smokers and we
wanted our message to be clear for them to stop smoking.
I also redesigned the interactive inforgraphics on the website too.
To create the design for the website I used Adobe Illustrator and Adobe
